query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, COUNT(s.id) as subjects_count 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON s.userId = u.id 
GROUP BY u.id 
HAVING subjects_count > 0 
LIMIT 5;
